=== Procedure ===
1. Enable "EFI Network Stack" in the BIOS. <br>
[[File:EFI_Network_Bios_Setting.PNG]]

2. Get into the [[EFI Shell]]

3. Run:
 ifconfig -s eth0 dhcp
[[File:EFI DHCP eth0.PNG]]

4. Run ifconfig for verification:
 ifconfig -l eth0
[[File:EFI ifconfig l.PNG]]


WARNING: Mixing TCP/IP stacks from other sources might cause unknown effects.
